<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF6F6AD0FF8C90D51A1DBDE7" pageId="148" pageNumber="909" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF6F6AD0FF8C90D51A1DBDE7" blockId="148.[109,1317,897,1907]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF6F6AD0FF8C90D51D37BD9F" bold="true" box="[112,823,1676,1709]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
The Fang He Tube-nosed Bat has been reported roosting alone or in small groups of 2-3 individuals.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
