<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF6F6AD0FE2390B91C14BDCF" box="[479,532,1760,1789]" country="Cameroon" name="North" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">Not</collectingRegion>
assessed on The IUCN Red List, due to its recent recognition as a species. The Fang He Tube-nosed Bat is currently known from only four specimens at two localities. It occurs in Fanjing Mountain National Nature Reserve.
</paragraph>
